Get available years for Wyoming enrollment data

Source: R/utils.R
get_available_years.Rd

Returns a vector of years for which enrollment data is available.

Usage

get_available_years()

Value

Integer vector of available years

Examples

get_available_years()
#>  [1] 2000 2001 2002 2003 2004 2005 2006 2007 2008 2009 2010 2011 2012 2013 2014
#> [16] 2015 2016 2017 2018 2019 2020 2021 2022 2023 2024
